channel.title: Azerothia742! NEW
channel.description:
Hi everybody! My name is Demon. Me and my friend have started a new server for you guys to enjoy! The revision is 742 and it has alot of EoC items and NPC's Our server has perfect PvP/PvM. So whatever your taste is, It will surely be filled on our magnificent server! I'm working on forums and a webclient as you're reading this. So be sure to stop on by today. I'm on mostly all day, Because I work from home.
Our server has alot of boss teleports, Above 15! And 10 PvP Teleports including Revenants with their PvP Armor drops!
Come on by and play awhile!
